<style>
   body{
       opacity:0;
   }
   </style>
     
     <script>
     function waitForElement(selector, callback, ms) {
     var maxCount = ms;
     var checkExist = setInterval(function () {
       maxCount -= 20;
     
       if (document.querySelector(selector) !== null) {
         clearInterval(checkExist);
         callback();
       } else if (maxCount <= 0) clearInterval(checkExist);
     }, 10);
     }
     document.heUpdateSaverBanner = {
     CTAText : 'Open an account',
     replaceBanner : function replaceBanner() {
       waitForElement(".sticky-start__btn.btn-primary", function () {
         var _bannerSection = document.querySelector(".sticky-start__btn.btn-primary");
         if(_bannerSection.innerText == "" || _bannerSection.innerText == null)
         {
         _bannerSection.innerHTML = document.heUpdateSaverBanner.CTAText;
         }
       });
       document.body.style.opacity = 1;
     },
     addAnalyticsTracking: function addAnalyticsTracking(){
       
     }
     };
     try {
         document.heUpdateSaverBanner.replaceBanner();
         setTimeout(function () {
           document.body.style.opacity = 1;
         }, 5000);
     } 
     catch (error) {
         console.log(error);
         waitForElement("body", function () {
         setTimeout(function () {
           document.body.style.opacity = 1;
         }, 1000);
       });
     }
     finally{
       waitForElement("body", function () {
         setTimeout(function () {
           document.body.style.opacity = 1;
         }, 1000);
       });
     }
     </script>
